ActOceans Act
SubjectAnguniaqvia niqiqyuam Marine Protected Areas Regulations
PrecisANGUNIAQVIA NIQIQYUAM MARINE PROTECTED AREAS REGULATIONS in order to protect the marine ecosystem, species and ecological processes in the Anguniaqvia niqiqyuam Marine Protected Area (ANMPA) so as to achieve its conservation objectives. This is accomplished through the prohibition of certain human activities in the ANMPA while allowing specific activities that are consistent with its conservation objectives.
